<p><font size="2">How would you like to know when your customers viewed your proposal, signed your purchase order or simply ignored your contract altogether – all from within Salesforce?  With EchoSign, you’ll have complete visibility into all of your contracts from within Salesforce.  Plus, signed contracts are automatically uploaded to your account and copies emailed to you and your customer.</font></p>
<p><font size="2">No more waiting by fax machines wondering if you should call.  No more questions as to if, when or what is signed.  You’ll be able to remind your customer or thank your customer, punctually and appropriately.</font></p>
<p><font size="2">With EchoSign, you’ll know immediately when the deal goes from “proposed” to “closed.”</font></p>
